{"tid":2180562,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"BLM起因 George Floyd命案涉事白人警察要求撤告指「他死於毒品而非膝蓋」","createTime":"2020-08-30T03:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-30T03:52:04.000Z","uid":28765,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a0159920ec9106359c7e5e79c58fa5a0cfd5df01","tid":2180562,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:10:05.000Z","msg":"〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國非裔男子佛洛伊德（George Floyd）5月遭到白人警察蕭文（Derek Chauvin）單膝壓頸8分鐘致死後，全美爆發「黑人的命也是命」（Black lives matter，BLM）示威風潮，後續影響現仍持續。不過事件主嫌蕭文卻於上週五（28日）要求法官撤銷對他的謀殺指控，指稱佛死於毒品作用而非壓頸動作。<br />\n<br />\n根據《每日郵報》報導，蕭文的律師於上週五（28日）在法庭上提出一項動議，聲稱佛洛伊德雖然因心臟驟停而死，但驗屍報告指出他本身患有高血壓性心臟病、動脈硬化等疾病，加上體內有芬太尼，以及使用甲基安非他命等，死因應是吸毒過量而非壓頸導致，「簡單地說，弗洛伊德先生無法呼吸，因為他攝入芬太尼的致死劑量」，要求法官撤銷對他的客戶的謀殺罪名。<br />\n<br />\n報導提到，佛洛伊德家族的律師本&middot;克魯普（Ben Crump）則表示，這次動議是一次「不法分子的不法之舉」，「全世界都看到事情是怎麼發生的，影片已說明了一切」<br />\n<br />\n&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;&middot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3275939\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3275939&d=XjGeTWWNN7bjI%2BfZ7PvsLCrXKCTJ71YGEIw5q99tfRY%3D&h=a0e46fa5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3275939&h=82f33418\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3275939</a>"},{"pid":"1bfb1963185ec4e399facbe36eaf602fe2175cab","tid":2180562,"uid":287422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-30T03:19:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c0354c21f6d8607838ff9c23cb511f6c64ff6d7","tid":2180562,"uid":21141,"lik